_sText:
This map is fully custom with the use of the real world textures pack.
This map has a Shot-for-Shot/Deagle Toss room, Pool, Showers, Locker Room, Maze, CT VIP w/ surveillance cameras, Cells, 2 Solitaries, T VIP, and a Big Cage.
I Hope you like It please leave feedback with your ideas and suggestions or just to give me your support :D I will continue to update, BUT I NEED THOSE IDEAS.


UPDATE: I added a few more things, Rearranged the Cells and added 4, Maze is Now OUTSIDE, The sky is SUNNY :D, As asked by request There are two bars...Should be easy to find.

V2.1 UPDATE: fixed somethings and is now 9MB SMALLER THAN V2!!!!!!!!!
